Each Awesomenaut can be upgraded with their own unique items to suit different strategies. Expect new items and Awesomenauts to be added regularly!<br><br>Inspired by animated series from the '80, this game brings the popular multiplayer battle arena (MOBA) genre to the 2D plane.<br><br>'It plays great and looks even better!' – Destructoid<br><br>'Awesomenauts has tons of humor and personality.' - Geekscape<br><br>You like Awesomenauts?
